<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٥٥ - <span class="c2">(١٩٩٧)</span> حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5898">مُحَمَّدُ بْنُ الْمُثَنَّى،</a> <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5509">وَابْنُ بَشَّارٍ </a>قَالَا: حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5532">مُحَمَّدُ بْنُ جَعْفَرٍ </a>، حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2779">شُعْبَةُ </a>، عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/4423">عُقْبَةَ بْنِ حُرَيْثٍ </a>قَالَ: سَمِعْتُ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3807">ابْنَ عُمَرَ </a>يَقُولُ: <span class="c2">« نَهَى رَسُولُ اللهِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></span></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>⦗٩٧⦘<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="special">ﷺ</span> عَنِ الْجَرِّ وَالدُّبَّاءِ وَالْمُزَفَّتِ،<span class="c5"> وَقَالَ:</span> انْتَبِذُوا فِي الْأَسْقِيَةِ .»<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>